headline: Regency Centers (REG) Q4 FFO Match Estimates
summary: Regency Centers (REG) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of +0.09% and +2.33%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Regency Centers: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The real estate investment trust, based in Jacksonville, Florida, said it had funds from operations of $219.3 million, or $1.17 per share, in the period. The average estimate of eight analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $1.17 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.
